---
const agentCommand = 'Read https://bmblx.bmi.osumc.edu/onboard/skill.md and follow the instructions to connect to CATION AI';
---

<section id="get-started" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
    <div class="w-5 h-px bg-scarlet-500"></div>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-scarlet-500">Onboarding</p>
  </div>
  <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
    Start in 30 seconds
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-3 text-slate-500 max-w-lg">
    Tell your AI coding agent to configure itself. No manual setup.
  </p>

  <!-- Agent command block -->
  <div class="mt-10 bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-6 lg:p-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/80"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/80"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400/80"></div>
      <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono">agent</span>
    </div>
    <div class="relative">
      <pre class="font-mono text-sm lg:text-base leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-wrap break-words pr-16"><code><span class="text-slate-500">$</span> {agentCommand}</code></pre>
      <button
        data-copy
        data-text={agentCommand}
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 hover:text-white border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 transition-colors cursor-pointer"
      >
        copy
      </button>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-slate-500">
      Works with OpenCode, Claude Code, Cursor, and any agent that can read URLs.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Manual steps -->
  <details class="mt-6 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors list-none flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="text-slate-300 transition-transform group-open:rotate-90 inline-block text-xs">&#9654;</span>
      Manual setup
    </summary>
    <div class="mt-5 pl-5 border-l-2 border-slate-200 space-y-5">
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm mb-1">1. Install OpenCode</p>
        <code class="text-sm font-mono text-slate-400">curl -fsSL https://opencode.ai/install | bash</code>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm mb-1">2. Install oh-my-opencode</p>
        <code class="text-sm font-mono text-slate-400">bunx oh-my-opencode install</code>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm mb-1">3. Get your API key</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Contact your lab admin (Cankun) for a virtual key with your budget allocation.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm mb-1">4. Let your agent do the rest</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Paste the command above into your agent — it reads skill.md and configures everything.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>
</section>
